{"tid":2437332,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「高登先」曾麗芬掟錢撐本土電影：疫情期間要倒貼，總之出到糧畀同事就可以","createTime":"2021-03-07T21:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T03:27:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcda79cbb937fd8d576f1845a8638a33663116c","tid":2437332,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T21:21:33.000Z","msg":"有人口裏說愛香港，身體卻很誠實；Golden Scene高先電影老闆曾麗芬（Winnie Tsang）從沒擺出高姿態，但卻出錢出力支持《狂舞派》系列、《幻愛》等本土電影，扶持香港新導演。<br />\n<br />\n《狂舞派3》更特別用上廣東話字幕，她連旗下的高先電影院小食部亦力求本土化，講到明：「我哋都希望幫助本地人，無論做邊一個行業，同埋希望有本土特色。疫情期間要倒貼，總之出到糧畀同事就可以。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_778119_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_778119_0&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058h5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=314b7f08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_778119_0&h=22cc8553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_778119_0</a>"},{"pid":"6bdd5980a8e33031c65448236d06dd681c6e437f","tid":2437332,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992768e2bfa39222bcdf37540e7f14fe4b273ed9","tid":2437332,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e76e6134eddebf4f0bb07dcd2332f051a664b4","tid":2437332,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:47:26.000Z","msg":"遠少少都值得去支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006604aef3369fead6ec666042a7569d7e2fa6c4","tid":2437332,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T01:34:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fc2f43d5810d5797963dd5ddb26ca1f6ac32df3e","tid":2437332,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T01:36:22.000Z","msg":"唔撐高先仲撐邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7a5f477a28c47e404462e9cd73d65b875d5cf1","tid":2437332,"uid":279463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T01:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65c273a2e21539b7c49fedb46469a25f4503345","tid":2437332,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:42:04.000Z","msg":"Golden Scene我以為係古仔開....? 唔係?"},{"pid":"0ac5916fa94727ce6112eb9e36c04ca7f2740ceb","tid":2437332,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a65c273a2e21539b7c49fedb46469a25f4503345","tid":2437332,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:42:04.000Z","msg":"Golden Scene我以為係古仔開....? 唔係?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"應該唔係<br />\n古天樂無開戲院<br />\n只係得香港藝術中心有個小型嘅「古天樂電影院」<br />\n專播一啲主流戲院唔播嘅小眾戲<br />\n咁當然<br />\n古天樂有無暗中幫高先戲院就唔知<br />\n佢近幾年都低調幫咗好多本地電影人<br />\n但無開聲宣傳自己"}]}